des:
Listen to this interactive story with a timeless lesson. 
Ever felt like the sacrificial lamb, waiting at the altar to be consumed mercilessly by a consumerist economy and a cancerous society? Then listen on to the story of a little mouse you name who realizes, he was bred for food to hungry pet snakes, listen on as he prays to be taken away by the Lord to another realm of quantum existence, a world of the spirit from this meager existence as meat.
At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
